### 1. 尝试预订 1 号滑板车 (成功路径)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/bookings/place
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": 1,
  "scooterId": 1,
  "totalCost": 15.50
}

### 2. 再次预订同编号滑板车 (应该失败，因为1号车已经被占用)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/bookings/place
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": 2,
  "scooterId": 1,
  "totalCost": 10.00
}

### 3. 查看 1 号用户的预订记录
GET http://localhost:8080/api/bookings/user/1